      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Chris Moreton</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:232px;\"><a href=\"/File:ChrisMoreton.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/c/c0/ChrisMoreton.jpg\" width=\"230\" height=\"230\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:ChrisMoreton.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Chris Moreton <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Chris Moreton</b>,<br />\na British computer scientist, B.Sc. in Computing and Informatics from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plymouth_University\">Plymouth University</a> in 1996, \nsoftware and web application developer. \nAlong with <a href=\"/Russell_Newman\" title=\"Russell Newman\">Russell Newman</a>, Moreton has developed and maintains the <i>Red Hot Pawn</i> correspondence chess site \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, \nand is co-author of the chess engine <a href=\"/Rival\" title=\"Rival\">Rival</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chris_Moreton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/3Xd8OM2Pwec/FTelUbCcPS4J\">Rival Chess 1.5.041</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chris Moreton</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, November 03, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/oM5FT21uIOg/YpA4IUZz6B4J\">public aplogoy/warning</a> by <a href=\"/James_Swafford\" title=\"James Swafford\">James</a> and Amy Long, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, November 19, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=39692\">History Heuristic on its own</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chris Moreton</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 16, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/History_Heuristic\" title=\"History Heuristic\">History Heuristic</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chris_Moreton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chrismoreton.com/\">Chris Moreton - JVM Developer (Java/Kotlin/Clojure/Scala)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/christopher-moreton/\">Chris Moreton | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/chris-moreton\">chris-moreton (Chris Moreton) · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.redhotpawn.com/\">Play Chess on RedHotPawn.com</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.redhotpawn.com/rival/programming/index.php\">Chess Programming - Introduction</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20160314001240/http://www.afewmorelines.com/understanding-magic-bitboards-in-chess-programming/\">Understanding magic bitboards in chess programming</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>) by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chris Moreton</a> in his programming blog, August 07, 2013 </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chris_Moreton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/chris-moreton\">chris-moreton (Chris Moreton) · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.redhotpawn.com/\">Play Chess on RedHotPawn.com</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20160313201136/http://www.rivalchess.com/about\">Rival Chess Engine - About</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301133730\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.013 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 57/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 130/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:7930-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301133730 and revision id 25301\n -->\n"
